{"tid":1586131,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不戴上豬咀眼罩，如何救港？戴上了豬咀眼罩，如何愛你...？","createTime":"2019-09-21T20:27:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T00:54:01.000Z","uid":237112,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c4f9d54fa199c550ca57f1565148a0b0f06066","tid":1586131,"uid":237112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:27:23.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢動了心，可以點？<br />\n<br />\n本來每日只係諗會唔會比狗咬，依家仲要諗埋你，我可以如何抉擇？<br />\n<br />\n我怕萬一唔小心比狗咬，冇得再見你，<br />\n也許要等到成功嘅一日先可以同你講出我嘅心意。<br />\n<br />\n若最後我分到常人戀愛運氣，到時我會用我真身愛你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家聽我呻，各位香港人，加油。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命 五大訴求 缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"e6c4c6b92674cb955c052a098d635a03d20edd65","tid":1586131,"uid":143319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:28:52.000Z","msg":"相約煲底 除罩相見"},{"pid":"17cc9e00621d920082460bf84993d3526bf4e8f7","tid":1586131,"uid":162215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:29:06.000Z","msg":"加油 期待煲底之日"},{"pid":"26490f20370c6df9b25d7cc2f970d0b8def4f7fe","tid":1586131,"uid":70979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5df5232456653fc40db8c14144738645657ef76","tid":1586131,"uid":325353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T20:32:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27edf150c5fbabebf2f6cae5962ab949f9b74f50","tid":1586131,"uid":308507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T00:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}